<h3>The Location Modifier Rule</h3>
<p>Photography is local. Every core keyword needs a city or neighborhood modifier.</p>
<p>Pattern: <code>[specialty] photographer [city]</code></p>
<p>Examples:
- "wedding photographer Austin TX"
- "headshot photographer Denver"
- "newborn photographer near me"</p>
<p>If you serve multiple cities, create a dedicated landing page for each. Do not stuff 5 city names into one page. Google rewards pages that focus on a single location with genuine local content.</p>
