<h3>Speed Optimization</h3>
<p>Photography sites routinely fail <a href="/blog/improve-core-web-vitals/">Core Web Vitals</a> tests. Common fixes:</p>
<ul>
<li>[ ] Convert all images to WebP or AVIF format</li>
<li>[ ] Enable browser caching</li>
<li>[ ] Minimize CSS and JavaScript files</li>
<li>[ ] Use a CDN (content delivery network) for image serving</li>
<li>[ ] Lazy load all below-the-fold images</li>
<li>[ ] Optimize the hero image on every page (it determines your LCP score)</li>
</ul>
<p>Test your site with <a href="https://pagespeed.web.dev/">Google PageSpeed Insights</a>. Target a mobile performance score of 70 or higher.</p>
